---
import SidebarLayout from '../../../layouts/SidebarLayout.astro';
import "../../../styles/global.css";
---

<SidebarLayout app="html">
  <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-5 text-custom-accent text-center">
    Links & Anchors
  </h1>

  <section class="mb-5 space-y-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-custom-secondary">
    <p>
      Links (hyperlinks) are what make the web "web-like." They allow users to navigate between pages, jump to specific sections, and access external resources.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Basic Link Syntax</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`<!-- External link -->
<a href="https://www.example.com">Visit Example.com</a>

<!-- Internal link to another page -->
<a href="about.html">About Us</a>

<!-- Link opening in new tab -->
<a href="https://example.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
  Open in New Tab
</a>

<!-- Email link -->
<a href="mailto:contact@example.com">Email Us</a>

<!-- Phone link -->
<a href="tel:+1234567890">Call Us</a>

<!-- Download link -->
<a href="document.pdf" download>Download PDF</a>`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Anchor Links & Page Navigation</h2>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`<!-- Creating anchor points -->
<section id="section1">
  <h2>Section 1</h2>
  <p>Content of section 1...</p>
</section>

<section id="section2">
  <h2>Section 2</h2>
  <p>Content of section 2...</p>
</section>

<!-- Navigation menu with anchor links -->
<nav>
  <a href="#section1">Jump to Section 1</a>
  <a href="#section2">Jump to Section 2</a>
  <a href="#">Back to Top</a>
</nav>

<!-- Link to specific section on another page -->
<a href="page.html#specific-section">Go to Specific Section</a>`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mb-3">Link Attributes & Best Practices</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
        <li>Use descriptive link text (avoid "click here")</li>
        <li>Add <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">rel="noopener noreferrer"</code> for security with <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">target="_blank"</code></li>
        <li>Use <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">title</code> attribute for additional context</li>
        <li>Make link destinations clear to users</li>
        <li>Ensure color contrast meets accessibility standards</li>
        <li>Test all links regularly</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SidebarLayout>